        EXAMPLES::

            sage: k.<a> = FiniteField(3^2, impl='pari_ffelt')
            sage: pol = a.polynomial()
            sage: pol
            a
            sage: parent(pol)
            Univariate Polynomial Ring in a over Finite Field of size 3

        ::

            sage: k = FiniteField(3^4, 'alpha', impl='pari_ffelt')
            sage: a = k.gen()
            sage: a.polynomial()
